  <brief_title>Near Infrared Spectroscopy to Determine Patent Ductus Arteriosus Closure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of Near Infrared Spectroscopy in Preterm Infants to Determine Patent Ductus Arteriosus Closure Following Medical Treatment</official_title>
  <sponsors>
